@page "/layout/breakpoints"

<PageTitle>Breakpoints - Tavenem Blazor Framework</PageTitle>

<Heading Level="HeadingLevel.H1">Breakpoints</Heading>

<p>
    The Tavenem Blazor Framework uses a set of 5 breakpoints to help design responsive layouts for
    devices of different sizes.
</p>

<p>
    Various utility classes can have a breakpoint infix applied to apply the class's styles only
    when the viewport is at least as large as the breakpoint specifies.
</p>

